com.crawljax.core.plugin

Interface PreCrawlingPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Plugin

    public interface PreCrawlingPlugin
extends Plugin
    Plugin that is called before the crawling starts and before the initial URL has been loaded. This kind of plugins can be used to do for example 'once in a crawlsession' operations like logging in a web application or reset the database to a 'clean' state.
